news.title: InDex Pharmaceuticals Enrolls First Patient in the Phase IIb Study CONDUCT With Cobitolimod
news.summary: /PRNewswire/ -- InDex Pharmaceuticals Holding AB (publ) today announced that the first patient has been enrolled in the clinical study CONDUCT - a phase IIb dose optimisation study with the drug candidate cobitolimod.
